            Verify phase proven before the bench exists.
            87: strong. SEL technical paper "Percentage Restrained Differential, Percentage of What?"
            (Thompson), read in full. Publishes TWO competing restraint definitions real relays
            actually use (AVERAGE vs MAXIMUM) + worked numeric tables. The bench MUST pick one and
